WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.170
Myocarditis results from viral infection, autoimmune

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:06.339
activation, or direct toxic injury to

00:00:06.339 --> 00:00:07.396
the myocardium.

00:00:07.396 --> 00:00:10.565
The inflammatory cascade activates resident macrophages

00:00:10.565 --> 00:00:13.735
and infiltrates lymphocytes into cardiac muscle.

00:00:13.735 --> 00:00:16.904
This triggers myocyte necrosis, interstitial edema,

00:00:16.904 --> 00:00:19.017
and progressive ventricular dysfunction.

00:00:19.017 --> 00:00:22.187
The result: reduced cardiac contractility and

00:00:22.187 --> 00:00:24.300
acute left ventricular dysfunction.
